BFN 

  [Text] Sevastopol, [No dateline as received] -- On 21 May a 
UNIAN correspondent learned from reliable sources that in the 
afternoon the Black Sea Fleet forces are planning to redeploy 51 
armored personnel carriers [APC's] from somewhere near 
Yevpatoriya to the vicinity of Sevastopol. These APC's from the 
composition of the coastal units will reinforce the Black Sea 
Fleet Marine Infantry. Relevant headquarters of a reinforced 
tank battalion and an antiaircraft missile battalion have 
already been formed. 

